"`6063`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:1841
msgid ""
"Added support for multiple standard values in :setting:`REFERRER_POLICY`. (:"
"issue:`6381`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:1844
msgid ""
"Added support for brotlicffi_ (previously named brotlipy_). brotli_ is still "
"recommended but only brotlicffi_ works on PyPy. (:issue:`6263`, :issue:"
"`6269`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:1850
msgid ""
"Added :class:`~scrapy.contracts.default.MetadataContract` that sets the "
