#: ../../../news.rst:2062
msgid ""
"The ``Authorization`` header is now dropped on redirects to a different "
"scheme (``http://`` or ``https://``) or port, even if the domain is the "
"same. Please, see the `4qqq-9vqf-3h3f security advisory`_ for more "
"information."
