#: ../../../news.rst:2907
msgid "Scrapy 2.7.1 (2022-11-02)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:2912
msgid ""
"Relaxed the restriction introduced in 2.6.2 so that the ``Proxy-"
"Authorization`` header can again be set explicitly, as long as the proxy URL "
"in the :reqmeta:`proxy` metadata has no other credentials, and for as long "
"as that proxy URL remains the same; this restores compatibility with scrapy-"
"zyte-smartproxy 2.1.0 and older (:issue:`5626`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:2921
msgid ""
"Using ``-O``/``--overwrite-output`` and ``-t``/``--output-format`` options "
"together now produces an error instead of ignoring the former option (:issue:"
"`5516`, :issue:`5605`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:2925
msgid ""
"Replaced deprecated :mod:`asyncio` APIs that implicitly use the current "
"event loop with code that explicitly requests a loop from the event loop "
"policy (:issue:`5685`, :issue:`5689`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:2929
msgid ""
"Fixed uses of deprecated Scrapy APIs in Scrapy itself (:issue:`5588`, :issue:"
"`5589`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:2932
msgid "Fixed uses of a deprecated Pillow API (:issue:`5684`, :issue:`5692`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:2934
msgid ""
"Improved code that checks if generators return values, so that it no longer "
"fails on decorated methods and partial methods (:issue:`5323`, :issue:"
"`5592`, :issue:`5599`, :issue:`5691`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:2941
msgid ""
"Upgraded the Code of Conduct to Contributor Covenant v2.1 (:issue:`5698`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:2943
msgid "Fixed typos (:issue:`5681`, :issue:`5694`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:2948
msgid "Re-enabled some erroneously disabled flake8 checks (:issue:`5688`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:2950
msgid ""
"Ignored harmless deprecation warnings from :mod:`typing` in tests (:issue:"
"`5686`, :issue:`5697`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:2953
msgid "Modernized our CI configuration (:issue:`5695`, :issue:`5696`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:2959
msgid "Scrapy 2.7.0 (2022-10-17)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:2963
msgid "Added Python 3.11 support, dropped Python 3.6 support"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:2964
msgid "Improved support for :ref:`asynchronous callbacks <topics-coroutines>`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:2965
msgid ""
":ref:`Asyncio support <using-asyncio>` is enabled by default on new projects"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:2967
msgid "Output names of item fields can now be arbitrary strings"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:2968
msgid ""
"Centralized :ref:`request fingerprinting <request-fingerprints>` "
"configuration is now possible"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:2974
msgid ""
"Python 3.7 or greater is now required; support for Python 3.6 has been "
"dropped. Support for the upcoming Python 3.11 has been added."
msgstr ""

