#: ../../../news.rst:4705
msgid "IPv6 support through :setting:`DNS_RESOLVER`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:4710
msgid ""
"Python 2 support has been removed, following `Python 2 end-of-life on "
"January 1, 2020`_ (:issue:`4091`, :issue:`4114`, :issue:`4115`, :issue:"
"`4121`, :issue:`4138`, :issue:`4231`, :issue:`4242`, :issue:`4304`, :issue:"
"`4309`, :issue:`4373`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:4715
msgid ""
"Retry gaveups (see :setting:`RETRY_TIMES`) are now logged as errors instead "
"of as debug information (:issue:`3171`, :issue:`3566`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:4718
msgid ""
"File extensions that :class:`LinkExtractor <scrapy.linkextractors.lxmlhtml."
"LxmlLinkExtractor>` ignores by default now also include ``7z``, ``7zip``, "
"``apk``, ``bz2``, ``cdr``, ``dmg``, ``ico``, ``iso``, ``tar``, ``tar.gz``, "
"``webm``, and ``xz`` (:issue:`1837`, :issue:`2067`, :issue:`4066`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:4724
msgid ""
"The :setting:`METAREFRESH_IGNORE_TAGS` setting is now an empty list by "
"default, following web browser behavior (:issue:`3844`, :issue:`4311`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:4727
msgid ""
"The :class:`~scrapy.downloadermiddlewares.httpcompression."
"HttpCompressionMiddleware` now includes spaces after commas in the value of "
"the ``Accept-Encoding`` header that it sets, following web browser behavior "
"(:issue:`4293`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:4732
msgid ""
"The ``__init__`` method of custom download handlers (see :setting:"
"`DOWNLOAD_HANDLERS`) or subclasses of the following downloader handlers  no "
"longer receives a ``settings`` parameter:"
