msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:4781
msgid ""
"The ``noconnect`` query string argument of proxy URLs is deprecated and "
"should be removed from proxy URLs (:issue:`4198`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../news.rst:4784
msgid ""
"The :meth:`next <scrapy.utils.python.MutableChain.next>` method of :class:"
"`scrapy.utils.python.MutableChain` is deprecated, use the global :func:"
"`next` function or :meth:`MutableChain.__next__ <scrapy.utils.python."
